      <body><!--			<div type="original" xlink:href="> --><!--			<div type="transcription" xlink:href="> -->
         <div type="edition" xml:lang="heb" subtype="transcription" xml:id="jeru0236.transcription">
            <p>
                    קינא עלמא עיבד ליסון בר פ   
                    <gap reason="illegible"/>
               <add place="above">אח</add> 
                    שלם די בנת לך קבור סבא הוה שלם
                    <lb/>
               <gap reason="illegible"/>
                    ס
                    <gap reason="illegible"/>
               <lb/>
                    כדנין 
                    קינא עלמא רחמיא למעבדא לך זי הוית שוא 
                    <gap reason="illegible"/> 
                    שלם
                    <lb/>
               <gap reason="illegible"/>
                    חני 
                    <gap reason="illegible"/>
                    סגי מח
                    <gap reason="illegible"/> 
                    קינא היכילין שלם</p>
         </div>
         <!--			<div type="translation" xlink:href="> -->
         <div type="translation" xml:id="jeru0236.translation">
            <p>A great lamentation he made for <name>
                  <persName xml:lang="grc " ref="persons.xml#jeru0236p01">Jason</persName>, <rs type="family">son of </rs> ...</name>, <rs type="family" ana="interpretations.xml#brother">brother </rs> (superscription), peace. Who built for you, elder, a grave,
                    may there be peace.... Similarly, a great lamentation dear ones will make for
                    you, that it would be... peace. <persName xml:lang="hbo " ref="persons.xml#jeru0236p02">Hani</persName>, greater than... a lamentation like these,
                    peace.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
